37.1 Métricas de clasificación binaria
\[
\text{accuracy}=\frac{TP+TN}{TP+TN+FP+FN}
\]
\[
\text{precision}=\frac{TP}{TP+FP}
\]
\[
\text{recall}=\frac{TP}{TP+FN}
\]
\[
F1 = 2\frac{\text{precision}\cdot \text{recall}}{\text{precision}+\text{recall}}
\]
